      "last_name": "Sudbury",
      "born_year": 1871,
      "bio": "Frederick Marcus Sudbury followed his father into the hosiery and glove manufacturing business.\n\nBetween 1 October 1891 and 9 January 1892, Frederick sailed to Sydney, Australia aboard the \"Macquaire\". His journal of the voyage, containing descriptions of Sydney and Melbourne, several sketches of sailing ships and kangaroos, and an abstract log of the return voyage (from 15 March to 19 July 1892), is held in the National Library of Australia.",
